  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9b0de1441a190476f84d46203267d169, type: 3}
  m_Name: ArtemQuestDialogue2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  Lines:
  - "Well, well. Took care of that idiot, huh."
  - "I\u2019m usually a bit rougher with guys like that\u2026 guess you decided to
    go easy on him."
  - "Either way \u2014 respect. Won\u2019t forget this. Although\u2026 next time,
    I\u2019ll probably handle it myself."
  - "Anyway, take care, my friend. I won\u2019t forget this."
  - "Yeah \u2014 grab your cigarettes. No problem. I can always get cigarettes for
    a friend."
